# Walkthrough — Chat Attachment Support

## Summary

Implemented end-to-end chat attachment support allowing users to upload multiple files (pdf, docx, txt, xlsx, png, jpg, jpeg) alongside chat messages. Files are saved to disk, recorded in the database, and linked to the user message.

